4chan Vocaroo URL replacer
by Scott Steiner <NothingFinerThanScottSteiner@gmail.com>
Updated by 666MAEDAEMON (https://store.steampowered.com/wishlist/id/MAEDAEFAE/)

October 2010 - September 2011
Updated 2026 :)

Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is 4chan Vocaroo URL replacer, a userscript for Firefox, Chrome and Opera.
It converts text or a link such as http://vocaroo.com/?media=vT1plxX90UX55rEGT, vocaroo.com/17luWJaGOLFi and https://voca.ro/17luWJaGOLFi
into an embedded object for easy playback.

You can now also click a button too load the embed rather than all the embeds just apearing :3

